      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example is a driver-focused machine with documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service already completed. The powertrain remains stock, retaining the factory individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response, while the variable M-differential provides exceptional lateral grip. The suspension geometry is tight, and the braking system has been recently refreshed with OEM components. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the internals and drivetrain are in excellent health, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
